A community app that makes supporting your favorite local businesses easy. Engaje allows a local business to engage with their customers effectively. Starting from Visit Logging to Transacting with local businesses, communities, clubs etc.

The Engaje app puts the power to support your favorite butcher, baker, café or greengrocer all in the same place. Just like when you go to the local shops they are all there. No need to struggle to find the right icon or the right website it even lets you support your local community clubs and schools by making them your favorites and amazingly it makes you a local wherever you go – check that out when you download.
descriptionShort: A community app that makes supporting your local businesses easy.
